---
// Personal — reading, coffee, writing. A bit more about me section.
//
// NOTE (Sridevi): book covers — save JPGs at
//   public/books/project-hail-mary.jpg
//   public/books/the-tainted-cup.jpg
// (grab covers from Goodreads, Amazon, or Open Library). Until those files
// exist, the book cover slots will show a placeholder.
---

<section id="personal" class="section-anchor border-t border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-50/50 dark:bg-neutral-950">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-content px-6 py-20 md:py-24">
    <p class="kicker mb-4">Personal</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
      A bit more about me
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-10 md:gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">

      <!-- Reading -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-ink-muted dark:text-neutral-400 mb-4">
          Reading
        </h3>
        <p class="text-ink-muted dark:text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mb-5">
          I read a lot &mdash; fiction mostly, plus a steady drip of non-fiction. My
          <a
            href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/26064783-sridevi-raghavan"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover dark:text-indigo-400 dark:hover:text-indigo-300 underline decoration-accent/40 underline-offset-2"
          >Goodreads</a>
          has the full archive.
        </p>

        <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-ink-subtle dark:text-neutral-500 mb-3">
          Recently finished
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <figure class="flex flex-col gap-2 w-24">
            <div class="aspect-[2/3] overflow-hidden rounded-sm bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800">
              <img
                src="/books/Project-Hail-Mary.png"
                alt="Project Hail Mary by Andy Weir"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <figcaption class="text-xs leading-snug text-ink-muted dark:text-neutral-400">
              Project Hail Mary<br/>
              <span class="text-ink-subtle dark:text-neutral-500">Andy Weir</span>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="flex flex-col gap-2 w-24">
            <div class="aspect-[2/3] overflow-hidden rounded-sm bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800">
              <img
                src="/books/Tainted-Cup.png"
                alt="The Tainted Cup by Robert Jackson Bennett"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <figcaption class="text-xs leading-snug text-ink-muted dark:text-neutral-400">
              The Tainted Cup<br/>
              <span class="text-ink-subtle dark:text-neutral-500">Robert J. Bennett</span>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Coffee -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-ink-muted dark:text-neutral-400 mb-4">
          Coffee
        </h3>
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden rounded-md bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 mb-4">
          <img
            src="/coffee.jpeg"
            alt="South Indian filter coffee"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="text-ink-muted dark:text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          South Indian filter coffee, almost daily. Steel tumbler, dabarah,
          thick decoction, boiling milk. Nothing else comes close.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Writing -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-ink-muted dark:text-neutral-400 mb-4">
          Writing
        </h3>
        <p class="text-ink-muted dark:text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mb-5">
          Two places I publish:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://themoneywellnessstudio.com/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-md border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 p-4 hover:border-neutral-300 dark:hover:border-neutral-700 transition"
            >
              <img
                src="/logo/the-money-wellness-studio.png"
                alt="The Money Wellness Studio logo"
                class="h-10 w-10 rounded object-contain shrink-0"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <span class="flex flex-col min-w-0">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink dark:text-neutral-100">
                  The Money Wellness Studio
                </span>
                <span class="mt-0.5 text-xs text-ink-muted dark:text-neutral-400">
                  Personal finance, written for real life.
                </span>
              </span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://impulsedinertia.substack.com/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="block rounded-md border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 p-4 hover:border-neutral-300 dark:hover:border-neutral-700 transition"
            >
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink dark:text-neutral-100">
                Impulsed Inertia
              </p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-ink-muted dark:text-neutral-400">
                Notes from building with AI &mdash; what works, what breaks.
              </p>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
